## MCP Tools Reference

| Tool                    | Description                   | Key Inputs                                                |
| ----------------------- | ----------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------- |
| `submit_vendor`         | Create a vendor record        | company_name, website, country, tech_stack, contacts, ... |
| `upload_document`       | Attach a document to a vendor | vendor_id, doc_type, filename, content_base64             |
| `run_assessment`        | Trigger 8-dimension scoring   | vendor_id                                                 |
| `get_assessment_status` | Poll assessment progress      | vendor_id                                                 |
| `get_report`            | Return full structured report | vendor_id                                                 |
| `list_vendors`          | Query vendor pipeline         | status?, risk_flag?, search?                              |
| `get_tasks`             | Get action items              | vendor_id?, department?, status?                          |
| `update_task`           | Change task status/assignee   | task_id, status, assigned_to?                             |
| `approve_vendor`        | Set cleared/rejected          | vendor_id, decision, reason                               |
| `get_analytics`         | Metrics and time-to-onboard   | from_date?, to_date?                                      |

## MCP Resources Reference

| Resource URI           | Description                         |
| ---------------------- | ----------------------------------- |
| `vendor://list`        | Live vendor pipeline snapshot       |
| `vendor://{id}/report` | Full assessment report for a vendor |
| `tasks://{department}` | Open tasks for a department         |

