## External APIs (Free Tier)

| API             | Purpose                        | Base URL                                           |
| --------------- | ------------------------------ | -------------------------------------------------- |
| NVD (NIST)      | CVE vulnerabilities            | `https://services.nvd.nist.gov/rest/json/cves/2.0` |
| Companies House | UK company registration data   | `https://api.company-information.service.gov.uk`   |
| OpenCorporates  | International company registry | `https://api.opencorporates.com`                   |
| OpenRouter      | LLM inference                  | `https://openrouter.ai/api/v1`                     |

- Cache all external API results in `enrichment_cache` table with 7-day TTL to avoid hammering free-tier limits.

